 "data": "@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam nodesep 100
skinparam ranksep 80

' --- STYLING (HIMS Blue Theme) ---
skinparam rectangle {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
 Padding 15
}
skinparam usecase {
 BackgroundColor #436FB6
 FontColor white
 BorderColor #2F528F
 FontSize 14
 Padding 15
}
skinparam database {
 BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
 FontColor #436FB6
 BorderColor #436FB6
 FontSize 13
}
skinparam arrow {
 Color #2F528F
 FontColor #444444
 FontSize 11
 MessageAlign center
}

' --- EXTERNAL ENTITY ---
rectangle \"Driver\" as Driver

' --- INTERNAL SUB-PROCESSES (The Breakdown of 2.0) ---
usecase \"2.1\nValidate Session\n& Status\" as P2_1
usecase \"2.2\nSanitize\nGPS Data\" as P2_2
usecase \"2.3\nUpdate Live\nDatabase\" as P2_3

' --- DATA STORES ---
database \"D1: Users\n(Driver Status)\" as D1
database \"D2: Live Logs\n(Coordinates)\" as D2

' --- ALIGNMENT ---
Driver -[hidden]down- P2_1
P2_1 -[hidden]down- P2_2
P2_2 -[hidden]down- P2_3

' --- DATA FLOWS ---

' Step 1: Input
Driver --> P2_1 : \" Incoming GPS Packet\"

' Step 2: Validation
P2_1 --> D1 : \"Check On-Duty Status\"
D1 --> P2_1 : \"Status OK\"
P2_1 --> P2_2 : \" Valid Session Token\"

' Step 3: Processing
P2_2 --> P2_2 : \"Remove Null/Zero Coords\"
P2_2 --> P2_3 : \" Clean Coordinates\"

' Step 4: Storage
P2_3 --> D2 : \"Write Latitude/Longitude\"
D2 --> P2_3 : \"Confirm Write Success\"

' Step 5: Feedback
P2_3 --> Driver : \" Update Acknowledged\"

@enduml",
 "format": "svg"
